text: Eleanor Roosevelt High School is a high school in Manhattan in New York City. Eleanor Roosevelt High School is made up with about 33 teachers and about 500 students from about 40 countries. The graduation rate of the school is 99% and 100% of the school has taken at least 1 AP exam. The school offers clubs such as the GSA Club and the Tech Club. == References == Category:Schools in New York (state)
title: Eleanor Roosevelt High School
